  "time_ut": 1659082773,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0db3\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd4 \u0db6\u0ddd\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd6 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who tried to sell a tear gas bomb was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Western Province South Crime Division says that a cook was arrested for selling a tear gas bomb that was stolen from police officers at Polduwa intersection in Battaramulla for 1000 rupees.",
        "On the 13th, while the officers of the Public Order Management Division were bringing tear gas bombs and bullets in a three-wheeler to control the protest at Polduwa intersection, a large group of people, including the arrested suspect, attacked the officers traveling in the three-wheeler and stole the bombs and bullets",
        "Nearly 385 tear gas shells and bombs were seized there",
        "At that time, the suspected cook stole a tear gas bomb and hid it in the restaurant in Battaramulla where he works.",
        "A police officer said that today (29) he went to the Maligawa road estate at the junction of the power plant and was arrested while he was returning from not being able to sell it.",
        "The police say that the arrested suspect was involved in the attack on the police officers traveling in the same three-wheeler and the attack on the army cab on the thirteenth.",
        "The arrested suspect, who is thirty years old and a resident of Matara area, is a drug addict",
        "On the advice of Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police in charge of Western Province Mr. Deshbandu Tennakoon, Deputy Inspector General of Garbage in charge Kapila Kadupitiya, Director of Western Province South Crime Division Senior Superintendent of Police Lalith Abeysekera Assistant Superintendent of Police Chandana Gamage, Station Commander of Western Province South Crime Division Inspector Jayantha Perera, Police Inspector Mr. Sumit Jayasinghe is conducting investigations"
      ],
